==分類和命名==
[[Image:Aloe_Vera.jpg|thumb]]：中國蘆薈(''Aloe vera'' var. ''chinensis'')]]
蘆薈的俗稱包含中國蘆薈、印度蘆薈、真蘆薈、巴貝多蘆薈等等<ref name="BPGE"/><ref name="Ombrello"/><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Liao Z, Chen M, Tan F, Sun X, Tang K | year = 2004 | title = Microprogagation of endangered Chinese aloe | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-cell-tissue-and-organ-culture_2004-01_76_1/page/83 | journal = Plant Cell, Tissue and Organ Culture | volume = 76 | issue = 1| pages = 83–86 | doi=10.1023/a:1025868515705}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/S0367-326X(99)00063-5 | vauthors = Jamir TT, Sharma HK, Dolui AK | year = 1999 | title = Folklore medicinal plants of Nagaland, India | journal = Fitoterapia | volume = 70 | issue = 1| pages = 395–401 }}</ref><ref name="Barcroft"/>，其種小名''vera''意思為「真」或「真正」<ref name="Ombrello"/>。有些文獻將有白點型態的蘆薈''Aloe vera''鑑定為其[[變種|變種]]中國蘆薈''Aloe vera'' var. ''chinensis''<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Wang H, Li F, Wang T, Li J, Li J, Yang X, Li J | title = [Determination of aloin content in callus of Aloe vera var. chinensis] | language = zh | journal = Zhong Yao Cai | volume = 27 | issue = 9 | pages = 627–8 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15704580 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Gao W, Xiao P | title = [Peroxidase and soluble protein in the leaves of Aloe vera L. var. chinensis (Haw.)Berger] | language = zh | journal = Zhongguo Zhong Yao Za Zhi | volume = 22 | issue = 11 | pages = 653–4, 702 | year = 1997 | pmid = 11243179 }}</ref>。然而從葉片的斑點來看種類會有廣泛變異<ref name="Akinyele"/>，因此有人提出斑點型態的蘆薈應與''Aloe massawana''同種<ref name=hb/>。此物種最初由[[卡爾·林奈|卡爾·林奈]]於1753年描述為''Aloe perfoliata'' var. ''vera''<ref>Linnaeus, C. (1753). ''Species plantarum, exhibentes plantas rite cognitas, ad genera relatas, cum differentiis specificis, nominibus trivialibus, synonymis selectis, locis natalibus, secundum systema sexuale digestas.'' Vol. 2 pp. [i], 561–1200, [1–30, index], [i, err.]. Holmiae [Stockholm]: Impensis Laurentii Salvii.</ref>，並在1768年由[[尼可拉斯·勞倫斯·伯曼|尼可拉斯·勞倫斯·伯曼]]於4月6日在''Flora Indica''一書中重新描述為''Aloe vera''。[[菲利普·米勒|菲利普·米勒]]亦在晚伯曼數十天後於''Gardener's Dictionary''書中描述其為''Aloe barbadensis''<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Newton LE | year = 1979 | title = In defense of the name ''Aloe vera'' | journal = The Cactus and Succulent Journal of Great Britain | volume = 41 | pages = 29–30 }}</ref>。

[[DNA|DNA]]比對認為蘆薈與[[葉門|葉門]]特有的[[索科特拉蘆薈|索科特拉蘆薈]]較為接近<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Darokar MP, Rai R, Gupta AK, Shasany AK, Rajkumar S, Sunderasan V, Khanuja SP | year = 2003 | title = Molecular assessment of germplasm diversity in ''Aloe'' spp. using RAPD and AFLP analysis | journal = J Med. Arom. Plant Sci. | volume = 25 | issue = 2| pages = 354–361 }}</ref>，從[[葉綠體|葉綠體]]的[[DNA序列|DNA序列]]比對以及[[微衛星|微衛星]]剖析亦顯示與''A. forbesii''、''A. inermis''、''A. scobinifolia''、''A. sinkatana''和[[線條蘆薈|線條蘆薈]]（''A. striata''）有緊密關係<ref name="Treutlein"/>。除了[[南非|南非]]種的線條蘆薈，上述蘆薈屬物種皆原產於[[索科特拉島|索科特拉島]]、[[索馬利亞|索馬利亞]]及[[蘇丹|蘇丹]] <ref name="Treutlein"/>。蘆薈缺乏明顯的自然群落以致部分學者認為可能是[[混種起源|混種起源]]<ref>Jones WD, Sacamano C. (2000) ''Landscape Plants for Dry Regions: More Than 600 Species from Around the World''. California Bill's Automotive Publishers. USA.</ref>。

蘆薈已廣泛培育在世界各處因而天然分布不詳。其歸化植株現蹤[[阿拉伯半島|阿拉伯半島]]的南半部，跨越[[北非|北非]]（[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]、[[茅利塔尼亞|茅利塔尼亞]]、[[埃及|埃及]]）以及[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]和其鄰國，直至[[加那利群島|加那利群島]]、[[維德角|維德角]]和[[馬德拉島|馬德拉島]]<ref name="AFPD"/>。這種分布與[[甜胶大戟|甜胶大戟]]、[[Pistacia_atlantica|Pistacia atlantica]]等其他物種有幾分相似，推測曾有大面積覆蓋的[[硬葉林|乾燥硬葉林]]因為[[撒哈拉|撒哈拉]]的[[沙漠化|沙漠化]]而劇減，留下獨立的植被區。許多關係緊密甚或相同的物種可見於撒哈拉的兩端：[[龍血樹屬|龍血樹屬]]和[[蓮花掌屬|蓮花掌屬]]便是兩個代表性例子。

蘆薈於17世紀引入中國和南歐各地<ref>Farooqi, A. A. and Sreeramu, B. S. (2001) ''Cultivation of Medicinal and Aromatic Crops''. Orient Longman, India. ISBN 8173712514. p. 25.</ref>。物種已廣泛歸化至各地包含溫帶或熱帶地區的[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]、[[巴貝多|巴貝多]]、[[貝里斯|貝里斯]]、[[庫拉索|庫拉索]]、[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]和美國的州如[[佛羅里達|佛羅里達]]、[[亞利桑那|亞利桑那]]和[[德克薩斯|德克薩斯]]<ref name="Akinyele"/><ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.hear.org/gcw/species/aloe_vera/| title= Global Compendium of Weeds ''Aloe vera'' (Aloeaceae)| publisher= Global Compendium of Weeds| accessdate= 2008-06-20| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080603031415/http://www.hear.org/gcw/species/aloe_vera/| archivedate= 2008-06-03| deadurl= no}}</ref>，其實際的物種分布已建議採用人類培育後的結果<ref name=hb/><ref>[http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=1&taxon_id=200027555 "Aloe vera (Linnaeus) Burman f., Fl. Indica. 83. 1768."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=1&taxon_id=200027555 |date=20170812190057 }} in ''Flora of North America'' Vol. 26, p. 411</ref>。

==種植==
[[Image:Aloe_vera_A.jpg|right]]]]
蘆薈已廣泛種植為觀賞植物，因其普遍被視為[[藥用植物|藥用植物]]和有趣的植物型態而流行於現代園藝中。肉質讓他們有能力存活在缺乏自然降雨的地區，成為假山和低用水花園的理想植物<ref name="Yates"/>。蘆薈的{{le|抗寒帶|Hardiness zone}}介於8-11，不耐重霜和雪 <ref name="BPGE"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/gardening/plants/plant_finder/plant_pages/7686.shtml|title=BBC Gardening, ''Aloe vera''|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate=2008-07-11|archive-date=2018-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021010142/http://www.bbc.co.uk/gardening/plants/plant_finder/plant_pages/7686.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。相對耐蟲害，但[[葉蟎科|葉蟎科]]、[[粉介殼蟲|粉介殼蟲]]、[[介殼蟲|介殼蟲]]和[[蚜蟲|蚜蟲]]等物種有可能造成植株的健康衰退<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.doacs.state.fl.us/pi/enpp/ento/a-myersi.html|title=Pest Alert: ''Aloe vera'' aphid ''Aloephagus myersi'' Essi.|publisher={{le|佛羅里達州農業暨消費者服務部|Florida Department of Agriculture and Consumer Services}}|accessdate=2008-07-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080612155315/http://www.doacs.state.fl.us/pi/enpp/ento/a-myersi.html|archivedate=2008-06-12|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mobot.org/gardeninghelp/PlantFinder/plant.asp?code=B628|title=Kemper Center for Home Gardening: ''Aloe vera''|publisher=Missouri Botanic Gardens, USA|accessdate=2008-07-11|archive-date=2005-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050527084103/http://www.mobot.org/gardeninghelp/PlantFinder/plant.asp?code=B628|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
種植於盆栽內需要在排水良好、砂質盆栽土壤和明亮日照的環境。蘆薈屬植物仍會因過多日照而焦褐或因排水不良枯萎，考量到排水性建議使用品質良好的增殖混合土或仙人掌和多肉植物混合土商品，[[陶瓦|陶瓦]]製的花盆也因多孔隙而受青睞<ref name="GA"/>。

盆栽需要完全乾涸後再澆水，花盆會因為蘆薈母植株旁生幼株變得擁擠，應當分株重新栽種以利生長也幫助避免病蟲害散播。冬天期間蘆薈可能進入休眠，此時需要少量濕氣。有降霜雪的區域最好將植株放置室內或[[溫室|溫室]]<ref name="BPGE"/>。蘆薈被許多國家以大規模農業生產來供應蘆薈凝膠給化粧品工業，如澳大利亞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2005/12/06/1524745.htm|title=''Aloe vera'' producer signs $3m China deal|publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate=2008-07-08|archive-date=2008-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205160200/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2005/12/06/1524745.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、孟加拉、古巴<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.invasor.cu/sistema/paginas/default.asp?lang=en&id=23062008_More%20Medicinal%20Plants%20Grow%20in%20Ciego%20de%20Avila|title=More Medicinal Plants Grow in Ciego de Ávila|publisher=invasor.cu|accessdate=2008-06-25}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>、多明尼加、中國、墨西哥<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dominicantoday.com/dr/economy/2006/7/7/15337/Korea-interested-in-Dominican-aloe-vera|title=Korea interested in Dominican 'aloe vera'|publisher=DominicanToday.com—The Dominican Republic News Source in English|accessdate=2008-07-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206062244/http://www.dominicantoday.com/dr/economy/2006/7/7/15337/Korea-interested-in-Dominican-aloe-vera|archivedate=2008-12-06}}</ref>、印度<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wildsingapore.com/news/20051112/051211-1.htm|title=India experiments with farming medicinal plants|publisher=channelnewsasia.com|author=Varma, Vaibhav|date=11 December 2005|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2006-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060324085032/http://www.wildsingapore.com/news/20051112/051211-1.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、牙買加<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20080117/eyes/eyes1.html|title=Harnessing the potential of our aloe|publisher=Jamaica Gleaner, jamaica-gleaner.com|accessdate=2008-07-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080324210301/http://www.jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20080117/eyes/eyes1.html|archivedate=2008-03-24}}</ref>、肯亞、坦尚尼亞、南非<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/200708020872.html|title=Kenya: Imported Gel Hurts Aloe Vera Market|publisher=allafrica.com|accessdate=2008-06-25|archive-date=2008-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206035233/http://allafrica.com/stories/200708020872.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及美國等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.resourceinvestor.com/pebble.asp?relid=38588|title=US Farms, Inc. – A Different Kind of Natural Resource Company|publisher=resourceinvestor.com|accessdate=2008-07-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080917125506/http://www.resourceinvestor.com/pebble.asp?relid=38588|archivedate=2008-09-17}}</ref>。

