===研究===
兩則2009年臨床研究的回顧判定沒有完善證據能得出強力的結論，但說明：“有初步的證據顯示口服蘆薈可能降低[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]患者的血糖和[[高血脂|高血脂]]患者的血脂，局部外用應無法防止輻射導致的皮膚損傷，而癒合傷口的相關證據則存在矛盾。需要更多和更好的詳細資料使這項熱門草藥的臨床效用更加精確<ref name="Vogler"/><ref name=Feily>{{cite journal | vauthors  = Feily A, Namazi MR | year = 2009 | title = ''Aloe vera'' in dermatology: a brief review | journal = G Ital Dermatol Venereol | volume = 144 | pages = 84–91 }}</ref>。”其中一則評論指出沒有證據顯示蘆薈屬植物能夠預防曬傷<ref name=Feily/>。一則2007年關於蘆薈燒燙傷應用的回顧指出「累積的證據傾向支持蘆薈用於一至二度[[灼傷|灼傷]]時能有效參與癒合，需要進一步設計良好的測試取得充分資料確定其產品效用<ref name=MaenthaisongEtal2007>{{cite journal | vauthors = Maenthaisong R, Chaiyakunapruk N, Niruntraporn S, Kongkaew C | title = The efficacy of aloe vera used for burn wound healing: a systematic review | journal = Burns | volume = 33 | issue = 6 | pages = 713–8 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17499928 | doi = 10.1016/j.burns.2006.10.384 | url = http://www.pha.nu.ac.th/nathorn/articles_PDF/13%20%20Aloe.pdf | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130718000125/http://www.pha.nu.ac.th/Nathorn/articles_PDF/13%20%20Aloe.pdf | archivedate = 2013-07-18 | access-date = 2016-03-19 }}</ref>。」蘆薈的局部應用也可能對[[生殖器疱疹|生殖器疱疹]]和[[乾癬|乾癬]]有效<ref name="Vogler"/><ref name="Deng2013">{{cite journal | vauthors = Deng S, May BH, Zhang AL, Lu C, Xue CC | title = Plant extracts for the topical management of psoriasis: a systematic review and meta-analysis | journal = Br. J. Dermatol. | volume = 169 | issue = 4 | pages = 769–82 | year = 2013 | pmid = 23909714 | doi = 10.1111/bjd.12557 }}</ref>。 一則2014年{{le|科克倫資料庫|Cochrane Library}}中的回顧指出沒有有力證據支持蘆薈在治療或預防[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]造成的[[靜脈炎|靜脈炎]]上的局部效用<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Zheng GH, Yang L, Chen HY, Chu JF, Mei L | title = Aloe vera for prevention and treatment of infusion phlebitis | journal = Cochrane Database Syst Rev | volume = 6 | issue = 6 | pages = CD009162 | year = 2014 | pmid = 24895299 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD009162.pub2 | publisher = [[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]] | subscription = yes }}</ref>。

蘆薈[[凝膠|凝膠]]在商業上用於[[優格|優格]]、[[飲品|飲品]]以及甜點<ref name="Reynolds"/><ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.abc.net.au/landline/stories/s502100.htm| title= Clean and green| author= Armstrong, Liza| publisher= Australian Broadcasting Corporation| accessdate= 2008-06-20| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080524205223/http://www.abc.net.au/landline/stories/s502100.htm| archivedate= 2008-05-24| deadurl= yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foodanddrinkeurope.com/news/ng.asp?n=18445-yagua-unveils-cosmeceutical|title=Yagua unveils cosmeceutical beverage|publisher=Decision News Media|accessdate=2008-06-20|archive-date=2020-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302000537/http://www.foodanddrinkeurope.com/news/ng.asp?n=18445-yagua-unveils-cosmeceutical|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。然而到達一定劑量無論口服或局部外用都可能有嚴重毒性<ref name="Expert Panel"/>。蘆薈的[[乳膠|乳膠]]亦同，過去曾用於[[青光眼|青光眼]]和[[多發性硬化症|多發性硬化症]]等病症直到[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]要求製造商停止使用<ref>{{cite web|title=Aloe|url=http://www.webmd.com/vitamins-supplements/ingredientmono-607-ALOE.aspx?activeIngredientId=607&activeIngredi1entName=ALOE|publisher=WebMD|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2017-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170328011716/http://www.webmd.com/vitamins-supplements/ingredientmono-607-ALOE.aspx?activeIngredientId=607&activeIngredi1entName=ALOE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===膳食補給===
{{le|蘆薈苷|Aloin}}是蘆薈屬植物的{{le|滲出液|exudate}}，在美國曾是[[非處方藥|非處方]][[瀉藥|瀉藥]]產品的常見成分，直到2002年才因製造公司無法提供必要的安全性資料遭[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]禁止<ref name="Nccih.nih.gov">{{cite web |url=http://nccih.nih.gov/health/aloevera |title=Aloe Vera : Science and Safety | NCCIH |publisher=Nccih.nih.gov |date= |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405080722/https://nccih.nih.gov/health/aloevera |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = | title = Status of certain additional over-the-counter drug category II and III active ingredients. Final rule | journal = Fed Regist | volume = 67 | issue = 90 | pages = 31125–7 | year = 2002 | pmid = 12001972 | author1 = Food Drug Administration | first1 = HHS }}</ref>。蘆薈有潛在毒性，攝取或外用達一定劑量有[[副作用|副作用]]<ref name="Expert Panel"/>，去除蘆薈苷後毒性可能降低<ref name="Boudreau"/><ref name="Vogler"/><ref name="Bottenberg MM, Wall GC, Harvey RL, Habib S 2007 1740–3">{{cite journal | vauthors = Bottenberg MM, Wall GC, Harvey RL, Habib S | title = Oral aloe vera-induced hepatitis | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-pharmacotherapy_2007-10_41_10/page/1740 | journal = Ann Pharmacother | volume = 41 | issue = 10 | pages = 1740–3 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17726067 | doi = 10.1345/aph.1K132 }}</ref>。
蘆薈汁市面上宣稱能幫助[[消化系統|消化系統]]健康，但沒有任何科學證據或監管部門認證<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/aloe-vera/NS_patient-aloe |title=''Aloe'' (''Aloe vera'') |publisher=MayoClinic.com |date=2012-09-01 |accessdate=2012-11-09 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102044911/http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/aloe-vera/NS_patient-aloe |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其抽取物和這類典型用途的毒性作用顯示具[[劑量依賴性|劑量依賴性]]<ref name="Expert Panel"/>。

===傳統藥用===
蘆薈傳統用於多種皮膚治療。在[[阿育吠陀|阿育吠陀]]中同[[龍舌蘭屬|龍舌蘭屬]]的萃取物稱為''kathalai'' <ref>Quattrocchi, Umberto (2012) ''CRC World Dictionary of Medicinal and Poisonous Plants: Common Names, Scientific Names, Eponyms, Synonyms, and Etymology'' (5 Volume Set) CRC Press. ISBN 978-1420080445</ref>{{rp|196、117頁}}。蘆薈早期的用法紀錄始於西元前16世紀的{{le|埃伯斯莎草紙|Ebers Papyrus}}<ref name="Barcroft"/>{{rp|18頁}}，以及西元一世紀中期[[迪奧科里斯|迪奧科里斯]]的[[藥物論|藥物論]]和[[老普林尼|老普林尼]]的[[博物志_(老普林尼)|博物志]]<ref name="Barcroft"/>{{rp|20頁}}，西元512年的{{le|維也納迪奧科里斯|Vienna Dioscurides}}中也有記載<ref name="Reynolds">Reynolds, Tom  (Ed.) (2004) ''Aloes: The genus Aloe (Medicinal and Aromatic Plants - Industrial Profiles''.  CRC Press. ISBN 978-0415306720</ref>{{rp|9頁}}。廣泛為各地的傳統藥草醫學所用<ref name="Boudreau"/><ref>{{Cite web|title = Top 10 Health Benefits of Aloe Vera ( Juice, Gel ) {{!}} NikiHow {{!}} How to - find best Article on Everything{{!}} Nikihow|url = http://www.nikihow.com/health-benefits-of-aloe-vera-juice-gel.html|website = www.nikihow.com|accessdate = 2016-01-06|archive-date = 2017-03-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170318015706/http://www.nikihow.com/health-benefits-of-aloe-vera-juice-gel.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

===商品===
蘆薈用在[[面紙|面紙]]上宣稱能保濕和減少刺激防止鼻子皮膚發炎。化妝品公司通常添加蘆薈的汁液或衍生物到產品中如化妝品、紙巾、保濕劑、肥皂、防曬乳、刮鬍泡或洗髮精等等<ref name="Reynolds"/>，一則學術文獻的回顧指出其含在許多衛生用品中的原因是“保濕潤膚的效果” <ref name="Eshun"/>。

萃取物的其他潛在用途包含稀釋綿羊人工授精的[[精液|精液]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Rodriguez F, Baldassarre H, Simonetti J, Aste F, Ruttle JL | title = Cervical versus intrauterine insemination of ewes using fresh or frozen semen diluted with aloe vera gel | journal = Theriogenology | volume = 30 | issue = 5 | pages = 843–54 | year = 1988 | pmid = 16726526 | doi = 10.1016/S0093-691X(88)80046-3 }}</ref>、新鮮食物的[[防腐劑|防腐劑]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Serrano M, Valverde JM, Guillén F, Castillo S, Martínez-Romero D, Valero D | title = Use of Aloe vera gel coating preserves the functional properties of table grapes | journal = J. Agric. Food Chem. | volume = 54 | issue = 11 | pages = 3882–6 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16719510 | doi = 10.1021/jf060168p }}</ref>、小型農場的[[節水|節水]]等<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/seta/2008/07/10/stories/2008071050161800.htm|title=Water conservation|accessdate=2008-07-14|publisher=The Hindu|location=Chennai, India|date=2008-07-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080802141458/http://www.hindu.com/seta/2008/07/10/stories/2008071050161800.htm|archivedate=2008-08-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>。蘆薈種子也被提議作為[[生物燃料|生物燃料]]的來源<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/Aloe-Vera-has-biodiesel-potential-reveals-MSU-study/324861/|title=''Aloe Vera'' has biodiesel potential, reveals MSU study|author=Shukla, S.|work=The Indian Express|accessdate=2008-06-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090114034759/http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/Aloe-Vera-has-biodiesel-potential-reveals-MSU-study/324861/|archivedate=2009-01-14}}</ref>。

==毒性==
外用蘆薈沒有明顯副作用<ref name="Nccih.nih.gov"/>，然而口服攝取可能造成[[腹痛|腹痛]]和[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]，反而能減少藥物的吸收<ref name="Nccih.nih.gov"/>。[[國際癌症研究機構|國際癌症研究機構]]研究發現蘆薈能使動物致癌，並表示也可能是人類致癌物<ref>[http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Preamble/CurrentPreamble.pdf Preamble] {{Wayback|url=http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Preamble/CurrentPreamble.pdf |date=20180328180246 }} in ''IARC Monographs on the Evaluation of Carcinogenic Risks to Humans''. [[國際癌症研究機構|國際癌症研究機構]], Lyon, France (2006)</ref>。

